The paper presents a new full-text index for compressing and encrypting nucleotide sequence collections in FASTA format and for performing fast pattern-search queries. This work involves data structures and algorithms for efficient indexing and searching of large genomic datasets, which are typically studied in computer science subfields such as data structures (cs.DS), databases (cs.DB), cryptography (cs.CR), information retrieval (cs.IR), and software engineering (cs.SE).
